title: Texas Health Huguley Cafeteria
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Buffet, Salad bar, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Daily vegan friendly salad bar. Meals prepared to Seventh Day Adventist standards; therefore, the cafeteria is mostly vegetarian with a few meat options. Veggie burgers and veggie breakfast meats are available daily. They do use eggs and cheese in some dishes. Wi-fi.
